ransitive test dependency for meaningful coverage. The javac failure is caused by an API/package relocation from janino's org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator to the transitive commons-compiler artifact's org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator, not missing setup.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No environment variables or system properties are required. Generated or adapted tests should use current Janino 3.1.0 APIs such as ExpressionEvaluator, ScriptEvaluator, ClassBodyEvaluator, SimpleCompiler, and the relocated org.codehaus.commons.compiler.util.iterator utilities when needed.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"Copying the existing 3.0.16 IterablesTest unchanged will continue to fail javac because org.codehaus.janino.util.iterator no longer exists in janino 3.1.0.\",\n    \"org.apache.ant:ant is optional/provided in the Janino POM and is only relevant if tests deliberately exercise AntCompilerAdapter; normal meaningful coverage should avoid requiring that optional dependency.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0062d78baeb77f75016a42f8d4bcc48197bef411dd86662f46\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1208, "output": 768, "cacheRead": 25088, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 27064, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782773964207, "responseId": "resp_0062d78baeb77f75016a42f8ccb0a08197beb05359f89fe130"}}
